"Generated Content" means any output produced by or through use of the Software, including but not limited to:
  a) AI-generated content, images, text, or data
  b) Derivative works incorporating such content
  c) Training data, model weights, or other AI artifacts
  d) Content created for streaming or social media platforms
  e) Modified or transformed versions of such content

"Training Data" means any data used to train, fine-tune, or otherwise modify AI models, including:
  a) Input data provided to the Software
  b) Output data generated by the Software
  c) Intermediate representations or embeddings
  d) Model weights or parameters
  e) Training logs and metadata

"Assessment Period" means:
  a) For revenue, valuation, and funding: Calendar quarters
  b) For user metrics: Rolling 3-month averages
  c) For content platform metrics: Monthly averages
  d) For streaming metrics: Daily peaks averaged over a month
  e) For social media metrics: 30-day rolling averages

